reviewText: Love this with my daughter and want to share with my students.

when my girls were younger, we would rent "Wee- sing" videos from the library all the time. They just loved watching them. So I just decided to look and see if I could possibly find these videos. What a treat it was when I actually found the wee sing videos. I am very happy with the "memory" video. It sure does bring back memories.
All of the Wee Sing Videos are a life saver. My 1 year old loves them. She been singing and dancing since she was 6 months old with them. Thank you for giving my wife and I time to have dinner ;-).
